609 auto &propStorage = this->sym_name;
610 return ::llvm::cast<::mlir::StringAttr>(propStorage);
611 }
612 void setSymName(const ::mlir::StringAttr &propValue) {
613 this->sym_name = propValue;
614 }
615 using usesBackVariablesTy = ::mlir::UnitAttr;
616 usesBackVariablesTy usesBackVariables;
617
618 auto getUsesBackVariables() {
619 auto &propStorage = this->usesBackVariables;
620 return ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<::mlir::UnitAttr>(propStorage);
621 }
622 void setUsesBackVariables(const ::mlir::UnitAttr &propValue) {
623 this->usesBackVariables = propValue;
624 }
625 bool operator==(const Properties &rhs) const {
626 return
627 rhs.builtin == this->builtin &&
628 rhs.function == this->function &&
629 rhs.generic == this->generic &&
630 rhs.params == this->params &&
631 rhs.sym_name == this->sym_name &&
632 rhs.usesBackVariables == this->usesBackVariables &&
633 true;
634 }
635 bool operator!=(const Properties &rhs) const {
636 return !(*this == rhs);
637 }
638 };
639protected:
640 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr odsAttrs;
641 ::std::optional<::mlir::OperationName> odsOpName;
642 Properties properties;
643 ::mlir::RegionRange odsRegions;
644public:
645 ComponentOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs = nullptr, const Properties &properties = {}, ::mlir::RegionRange regions = {});
646
647 ComponentOpGenericAdaptorBase(ComponentOp op);

649 std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize);
650 const Properties &getProperties() {
651 return properties;
652 }

2558 ::mlir::LogicalResult verifyInvariantsImpl();
2559 ::mlir::LogicalResult verifyInvariants();
2560 static ::mlir::ParseResult parse(::mlir::OpAsmParser &parser, ::mlir::OperationState &result);
2561 void print(::mlir::OpAsmPrinter &_odsPrinter);
2562private:
2563 ::mlir::StringAttr getAttributeNameForIndex(unsigned index) {
2564 return getAttributeNameForIndex((*this)->getName(), index);
2565 }
2566
2567 static ::mlir::StringAttr getAttributeNameForIndex(::mlir::OperationName name, unsigned index) {
2568 assert(index < 2 && "invalid attribute index");
2569 assert(name.getStringRef() == getOperationName() && "invalid operation name");
2570 assert(name.isRegistered() && "Operation isn't registered, missing a "
2571 "dependent dialect loading?");
2572 return name.getAttributeNames()[index];
2573 }
2574
2575public:
2576};

2999 return ::llvm::cast<::mlir::StringAttr>(propStorage);
3000 }

3002 this->value = propValue;

3005 return
3006 rhs.value == this->value &&
3007 true;

4956 return ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<::mlir::UnitAttr>(propStorage);
4957 }
4958 void setGeneric(const ::mlir::UnitAttr &propValue) {
4959 this->generic = propValue;
4960 }
4961 using paramsTy = ::mlir::ArrayAttr;
4962 paramsTy params;
4963
4964 auto getParams() {
4965 auto &propStorage = this->params;
4966 return ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<::mlir::ArrayAttr>(propStorage);
4967 }
4968 void setParams(const ::mlir::ArrayAttr &propValue) {
4969 this->params = propValue;
4970 }
4971 using sym_nameTy = ::mlir::StringAttr;
4972 sym_nameTy sym_name;
4973
4974 auto getSymName() {
4975 auto &propStorage = this->sym_name;
4976 return ::llvm::cast<::mlir::StringAttr>(propStorage);
4977 }
4978 void setSymName(const ::mlir::StringAttr &propValue) {
4979 this->sym_name = propValue;
4980 }
4981 using usesBackVariablesTy = ::mlir::UnitAttr;
4982 usesBackVariablesTy usesBackVariables;
4983
4984 auto getUsesBackVariables() {
4985 auto &propStorage = this->usesBackVariables;
4986 return ::llvm::dyn_cast_or_null<::mlir::UnitAttr>(propStorage);
4987 }
4988 void setUsesBackVariables(const ::mlir::UnitAttr &propValue) {
4989 this->usesBackVariables = propValue;
4990 }
4991 bool operator==(const Properties &rhs) const {
4992 return
4993 rhs.builtin == this->builtin &&
4994 rhs.function == this->function &&
4995 rhs.generic == this->generic &&
4996 rhs.params == this->params &&
4997 rhs.sym_name == this->sym_name &&
4998 rhs.usesBackVariables == this->usesBackVariables &&
4999 true;
5000 }
5001 bool operator!=(const Properties &rhs) const {
5002 return !(*this == rhs);
5003 }
5004 };
5005protected:
5006 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr odsAttrs;
5007 ::std::optional<::mlir::OperationName> odsOpName;
5008 Properties properties;
5009 ::mlir::RegionRange odsRegions;
5010public:

5012

5018 }

5843 this->computeOnly = propValue;

5846 return
5847 rhs.computeOnly == this->computeOnly &&
5848 true;
5849 }
5850 bool operator!=(const Properties &rhs) const {
5851 return !(*this == rhs);
5852 }
5853 };

6006class WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptorBase {
6007public:
6008 struct Properties {
6009 using field_nameTy = ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr;
6010 field_nameTy field_name;
6011
6012 auto getFieldName() {
6013 auto &propStorage = this->field_name;
6014 return ::llvm::cast<::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr>(propStorage);
6015 }
6016 void setFieldName(const ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr &propValue) {
6017 this->field_name = propValue;
6018 }
6019 bool operator==(const Properties &rhs) const {
6020 return
6021 rhs.field_name == this->field_name &&
6022 true;
6023 }
6024 bool operator!=(const Properties &rhs) const {
6025 return !(*this == rhs);
6026 }
6027 };
6028protected:
6029 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr odsAttrs;
6030 ::std::optional<::mlir::OperationName> odsOpName;
6031 Properties properties;
6032 ::mlir::RegionRange odsRegions;
6033public:
6034 WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptorBase(::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs = nullptr, const Properties &properties = {}, ::mlir::RegionRange regions = {});
6035
6036 WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptorBase(WriteFieldOp op);
6037
6038 std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index, unsigned odsOperandsSize);
6039 const Properties &getProperties() {
6040 return properties;
6041 }
6042
6043 ::mlir::DictionaryAttr getAttributes();
6044 ::mlir::FlatSymbolRefAttr getFieldNameAttr();
6045 ::llvm::StringRef getFieldName();
6046};
6047} // namespace detail
6048template <typename RangeT>
6049class WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptor : public detail::WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptorBase {
6050 using ValueT = ::llvm::detail::ValueOfRange<RangeT>;
6051 using Base = detail::WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptorBase;
6052public:
6053 WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptor(RangeT values, ::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs = nullptr, const Properties &properties = {}, ::mlir::RegionRange regions = {}) : Base(attrs, properties, regions), odsOperands(values) {}
6054
6055 WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptor(RangeT values, ::mlir::DictionaryAttr attrs, ::mlir::OpaqueProperties properties, ::mlir::RegionRange regions = {}) : WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptor(values, attrs, (properties ? *properties.as<Properties *>() : Properties{}), regions) {}
6056
6057 template <typename LateInst = WriteFieldOp, typename = std::enable_if_t<std::is_same_v<LateInst, WriteFieldOp>>>
6058 WriteFieldOpGenericAdaptor(RangeT values, LateInst op) : Base(op), odsOperands(values) {}
6059
6060 std::pair<unsigned, unsigned> getODSOperandIndexAndLength(unsigned index) {
6061 return Base::getODSOperandIndexAndLength(index, odsOperands.size());
6062 }
6063
6064 RangeT getODSOperands(unsigned index) {
6065 auto valueRange = getODSOperandIndexAndLength(index);
6066 return {std::next(odsOperands.begin(), valueRange.first),
6067 std::next(odsOperands.begin(), valueRange.first + valueRange.second)};
6068 }
6069
6070 ValueT getComponent() {
6071 return (*getODSOperands(0).begin());
6072 }
6073
6074 ValueT getVal() {
6075 return (*getODSOperands(1).begin());
6076 }
6077
6078 RangeT getOperands() {
6079 return odsOperands;
6080 }
6081
6082private:
6083 RangeT odsOperands;
6084};
